  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrc="shortdesc:1;7:29" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/common/reuse-w-lwdita/reuse-map.dita">A DITA map is the mechanism for aggregating topic references and
    defining a context for those references. It contains references to topics, maps, and other
    resources; these references are organized into hierarchies, groups, and tables.</shortdesc>
