<example class="- topic/example " id="example" otherprops="examples" xtrc="example:1;20:45" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/map.dita"><title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:5;20:52" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/map.dita">Example</title><p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:3;20:70" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/map.dita">The following code sample contains six <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:3;20:121" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/map.dita">topicref</xmlelement> elements. The
